<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to CasGists!</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #2c3e50; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .button { background-color: #3498db; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; }
        .features { background-color: white; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 style="margin: 0;">🚀 Welcome to CasGists!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello {{.UserName}}!</h2>
            
            <p>Welcome to your new CasGists instance - your personal code snippet management platform. We're thrilled to have you on board!</p>
            
            <div class="features">
                <h3>🌟 Get Started with These Features:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>📝 <strong>Create Gists</strong> - Share code snippets with syntax highlighting</li>
                    <li>🔒 <strong>Privacy Controls</strong> - Keep gists public, unlisted, or private</li>
                    <li>⭐ <strong>Star & Fork</strong> - Save and build upon others' work</li>
                    <li>👥 <strong>Collaborate</strong> - Work together with organizations</li>
                    <li>🔍 <strong>Powerful Search</strong> - Find code quickly</li>
                    <li>📱 <strong>Mobile Ready</strong> - Access from any device</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{.LoginURL}}" class="button">Start Creating Gists</a>
            </div>
            
            <h3>📚 Helpful Resources:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="{{.LoginURL}}/docs/quickstart">Quick Start Guide</a></li>
                <li><a href="{{.LoginURL}}/docs/api">API Documentation</a></li>
                <li><a href="{{.LoginURL}}/settings">Account Settings</a></li>
                <li><a href="{{.SupportURL}}">Support Center</a></li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Have questions? Just reply to this email or visit our <a href="{{.SupportURL}}">support center</a>.</p>
            
            <p>Happy coding!<br>
            The CasGists Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent to you because you created an account on CasGists.<br>
            <a href="{{.LoginURL}}/settings/notifications">Manage email preferences</a> | 
            <a href="{{.LoginURL}}/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>